quran[27{c,v,t}:
37,127,Fakazzaboohu fa inna hum lamuhdaroon
37,128,Illaa 'ibaadal laahil mukhlaseen
37,129,Wa taraknaa 'alaihi fil aakhireen
37,130,Salaamun 'alaaa Ilyaaseen
37,131,Innaa kazaalika najzil muhsineen
37,132,Innahoo min 'ibaadinal mu'mineen
37,133,Wa inna Lootal laminal mursaleen
37,134,Iz najjainaahu wa ahlahooo ajma'een
37,135,Illaa 'ajoozan fil ghaabireen
37,136,Summa dammarnal aakhareen
37,137,Wa innakum latamurroona 'alaihim musbiheen
37,138,Wa billail; afalaa ta'qiloon�(section 4)
37,139,Wa inna Yoonusa laminal mursaleen
37,140,Iz abaqa ilal fulkil mash hoon
37,141,Fasaahama fakaana minal mudhadeen
37,142,Faltaqamahul hootu wa huwa muleem
37,143,Falaw laaa annahoo kaana minal musabbiheen
37,144,Lalabisa fee batniheee ilaa Yawmi yub'asoon
37,145,Fanabaznaahu bil'araaa'i wa huwa saqeem
37,146,Wa ambatnaa 'alaihi shajaratam mai yaqteen
37,147,Wa arsalnaahu ilaa mi'ati alfin aw yazeedoon
37,148,Fa aamanoo famatta' naahum ilaa heen
37,149,Fastaftihim ali Rabbikal banaatu wa lahumul banoon
37,150,Am khalaqnal malaaa'i kata inaasanw wa hm shaahidoon
37,151,Alaaa innahum min ifkihim la yaqooloon
37,152,Waladal laahu wa innhum lakaaziboon
37,153,Astafal banaati 'alal baneen
